keys.string: Ryn is relaxing once again. He’s got his headphones in and is mouthing the lyrics to whatever song he’s listening to.
Ryn pulls out one of his earbuds as I approach.
Hey Ryn, what are you listening to?
You listen to him a lot?
Often. He might be one of my favorites since I keep coming back to listen to him. I’ll make you a playlist later if you want.
